Application Name: Lightning Gong
Version: 1.2.1
Category: Timer Tool
Author: Toshiharu Takematsu
Source: https://github.com/toshi3221/gong

Description
===========
This application will ring the gong repeatedly at a specified interval time.

History
=======
1.2.1, 01/01/2013 - Bug fix. See detail #1 and #2.
1.2,   07/20/2011 - If the total number of 1 has been changed to the total number of text does not appear.
                  Display time was changed from the total time to the time remaining.
1.1,   07/14/2011 - It was possible to set the total number of gongs.
1.0,   07/04/2011 - The first public version of the Android Market.
0.1,   06/22/2011 - Initial release.

